schools.name: Veterans Park Academy For The Arts

data.description: Beautiful pool home with 4 bedrooms and 2 baths. Special features include: screened saltwater pool with solar heat, three double sliders to the screened lanai with a kitchen pass-thru window to the covered porch, master with walk-in closet and a private office, cathedral ceilings, whole house central vacuum, rare front door closet, outdoor shower, keypad entry to double garage with built-in cabinets galore, city water and city sewer, playset stays in the 4' fenced in backyard. Located very near Lehigh Acres Middle School. Enjoy your very own orange tree.  Brand new GE washer and dryer, Haywood pool cleaner and pool pump (all 2023). This home is a must see for your family. Excellent neighborhood of high-end homes, 5 minutes to Publix!
